project_descr: PIMS 3277 CC PDFB – Market Transformation Through Energy Efficiency Standards and Labelling of Appliances in South Africa

outputs.output_descr: This project aims to reduce electricity demand due to households appliances, and in so doing also reduce greenhouse gas (GHG) emissions by developing and implementing S&L programs for 12 appliances.
